Explore the traditional Vedic ritual of Anulepna, or smearing of the divine with our Chandani Avahana Ubtan.

This creamy mousse is an exquisite blend of several clays, a secret Ubtan recipe made up of 14 potent natural herbs and ingredients like Green Clay, Mulberry Extracts, Sandalwood Oil,Silver leaf,along with a generous drizzle of beautifying oils like Evening Primrose Oil, Calendula Oil, Olive Oil, Bergamot Oil and special ingredients like Aloe Vera Extracts together they help deeply cleanse and rejuvenate the skin without stripping away its natural oil. 
It can be used as a face wash- face scrub or even a face mask.

This offering of ours is a tribute to the traditional beauty ritual of Anulepna with Ubtan- which is also done to the bride during the ceremony of Haldi often by her own family, friends and relatives.✨

From a first-generation immigrant battling countless obstacles to witnessing the dream of Global Beauty Secrets shine on NBC6's SFL Live – today is surreal. 💫

Baha Hibiscus Hair Dew, inspired by Princess Mrinalika's Santhali heritage and fortified with Ayurvedic herbs and potent science, isn't just a product; it's a tribute to perseverance and love. 😇

The scalp ages 12 times faster, but with Redensyl, Hibiscus, Gotu Kola, and Hydrolyzed Rice Protein, we aim to nourish it with clean actives and plant based wisdom. ✨

We are truly proud to get the “made in India” story to the global stage and back it up with good credibility. Dear USA, the stars on your flag gleam especially bright tonight, lighting up my childhood dreams. ❤️🧿

Here’s to Global Beauty Secrets bridging the beauty map. ❤️✨

Thank you for embracing us and our story.🌺🙏🏼
- Aishwarya S Nir

latestPosts.caption: Embrace the art of Japanese beauty rituals with our unique Adzuki Bean cleanser! ✨ Traditionally used for centuries, these gentle red beans provide a natural way to polish away dead cells and reveal smoother, brighter skin. Yet, finding the perfect balance matters—go too hard and you risk irritation, too gentle and the glow never shows. Our GB cleanser brings you the best of both worlds: finely milled Adzuki for effective exfoliation, paired with soothing aloe vera to keep your skin calm, nourished, and utterly radiant. It’s time to refine your routine and experience an ancient secret elevated for modern beauty. #AdzukiBeans #JapaneseSkincare #GlowingSkinRoutine #NaturalExfoliant #CleanBeauty #discovertogether
